<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Two-Factor Authentication Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #000000;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 24px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .code-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border: 2px solid #000000;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      color: #000000;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 32px 40px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .divider {
      margin: 32px 0;
      border: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .warning-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #991b1b;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>NEXST Starter Kit</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
      <p>You requested a two-factor authentication code. Use the code below to complete your login:</p>

      <div class="code-box">
        <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        This code will expire in 10 minutes
      </p>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <p><strong>Security Alert:</strong> If you didn't request this code, someone may be trying to access your account. Please secure your account immediately by changing your password.</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        For your security, never share this code with anyone. Our team will never ask you for your authentication codes.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 NEXST Starter Kit. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
